query:
INSERT INTO project_group_member
                (
                    project_group_id,
                    character_id,
                    accepted,
                    permission,
                    created_at,
                    updated_at
                )
                SELECT $1, * FROM UNNEST(
                    $2::INTEGER[],
                    $3::BOOLEAN[],
                    $4::INTEGER[],
                    $5::TIMESTAMPTZ[],
                    $6::TIMESTAMPTZ[]
                )
